meals or sleepovers...

28
00:01:22,165 --> 00:01:24,416
We shouldn't have
sleepovers. You snore.

29
00:01:25,936 --> 00:01:29,103
But mockery, I don't
know. That's a deal breaker.

30
00:01:29,205 --> 00:01:31,245
OK. Sex and mockery it is.

31
00:01:31,292 --> 00:01:32,835
<i>It would be too easy</i>

32
00:01:32,859 --> 00:01:35,060
<i>if it was just drugs and
booze and cigarettes.</i>

33
00:01:35,162 --> 00:01:38,062
She said she loved
me and you know what?

34
00:01:38,165 --> 00:01:41,934
My dad... Oh, God, he loved
her and... and, you know,

35
00:01:42,035 --> 00:01:46,355
when he died, then... I...

36
00:01:46,457 --> 00:01:48,977
I shouldn't have gotten married.

37
00:01:50,644 --> 00:01:55,229
<i>I think the hardest part of
kicking a habit is wanting to kick it.</i>

38
00:01:56,583 --> 00:02:00,786
<i>I mean, we get addicted
for a reason, right?</i>

39
00:02:00,887 --> 00:02:03,087
