40
00:02:05,892 --> 00:02:08,777
<i>♪ From my heart to yours ♪</i>

41
00:02:14,551 --> 00:02:17,319
I thought it was right,
but it wasn't. It's not.

42
00:02:17,421 --> 00:02:19,437
- It's not.
- No.

43
00:02:19,540 --> 00:02:24,142
<i>Often, too often, things that start
out as just a normal part of your life,</i>

44
00:02:24,244 --> 00:02:28,179
<i>at some point cross
the line to obsessive.</i>

45
00:02:28,281 --> 00:02:31,049
<i>Compulsive. Out of control.</i>

46
00:02:31,151 --> 00:02:33,985
I... I got to tell her.

47
00:02:34,087 --> 00:02:37,989
I have to tell her that the marriage
is over. It's the right thing to do.

48
00:02:40,594 --> 00:02:46,431
<i>♪ And there's no
denying our love is real... ♪</i>

49
00:02:46,533 --> 00:02:48,678
Did you see how I
walked out determined?

50
00:02:48,702 --> 00:02:50,752
