51
00:02:50,854 --> 00:02:53,438
<i>♪ From my heart to yours ♪</i>

52
00:02:53,541 --> 00:02:55,974
<i>It's the high we're chasing.</i>

53
00:02:56,076 --> 00:03:00,128
