- They weren't.

332
00:18:19,081 --> 00:18:22,260
When you cook meth, the
fumes coat the walls, the floors.

333
00:18:22,284 --> 00:18:25,163
The baby crawls around,
puts its hands in its mouth.

334
00:18:25,187 --> 00:18:27,388
