335
00:18:27,490 --> 00:18:29,690
Call the police
and social services.

336
00:18:29,792 --> 00:18:32,059
What about the
dad? He's still in there.

337
00:18:32,161 --> 00:18:35,124
Call the police. They
take care of the dad.

338
00:18:35,148 --> 00:18:38,982
You take care of the baby.
Sloan! We got a situation.

339
00:18:41,254 --> 00:18:42,836
You're doing a fine job.

340
00:18:42,938 --> 00:18:47,491
You were acting awfully odd
before. Had me a little nervous.

341
00:18:49,746 --> 00:18:52,113
Mr. Roche, I'm gonna
ask you a question.

342
00:18:52,215 --> 00:18:54,381
I don't want you
to be offended by it,

343
00:18:54,483 --> 00:18:57,100
but the answer could
affect your surgery.

344
00:18:57,203 --> 00:19:00,387
- Fine. Fire away.
- Are you
a crystal meth user?

345
00:19:00,489 --> 00:19:02,690
You're kidding,
