- Mrs. Burke!
- I don't think
I know you.

394
00:21:57,967 --> 00:22:01,852
I'm George O'Malley! I'm a
friend of Burke's. I was Burke's guy.

395
00:22:01,954 --> 00:22:05,206
Oh, hi, George O'Malley,

396
00:22:05,308 --> 00:22:08,125
Burke's friend,
Burke's guy. Please sit.

397
00:22:08,227 --> 00:22:10,110
I guess I have a minute.

398
00:22:12,581 --> 00:22:16,300
One time he let me live on his
sofa when I had no place else to stay.

399
00:22:16,402 --> 00:22:19,903
How is he? Is he OK?

400
00:22:20,005 --> 00:22:23,440
He's Preston. He's a gentleman.

401
00:22:23,542 --> 00:22:26,710
And so he doesn't
like to talk about it.

402
00:22:26,796 --> 00:22:31,064
And I just really don't
know what to say to him.

403
00:22:34,921 --> 00:22:38,255
Maybe, uh... I don't know.

404
00:22:38,357 --> 00:22:40,757
You could tell him
that he dodged a bullet.

405
00:22:40,859 --> 00:22:43,594
I mean, marriage is...

406
00:22:43,696 --> 00:22:46,546
Once you're in, you're in.

407
00:22:47,716 --> 00:22:50,951
Burke is smart, you know.
He didn't make a mistake.

408
00:22:51,053 --> 00:22:54,872
Because a mistake
that, you know...

409
00:22:54,974 --> 00:22:59,626
It's hard to take back. Which even
if you want to take back, you can't.

410
00:23:01,463 --> 00:23:03,113
So you can tell him that.

411
00:23:04,433 --> 00:23:06,933
"Once you're in, you're in."

412
00:23:08,037 --> 00:23:10,182
